---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Fajos TechBlog">
	<div class="about-content">
		<h1>About Fajos TechBlog</h1>
		<p>Welcome to Fajos TechBlog, your source for in-depth articles about web development, programming, and technology.</p>
		
		<h2>Our Mission</h2>
		<p>We aim to provide high-quality, educational content that helps developers stay up-to-date with the latest trends and best practices in the tech industry.</p>
		
		<h2>Topics We Cover</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Web Development</li>
			<li>Programming Languages</li>
			<li>Software Architecture</li>
			<li>Developer Tools</li>
			<li>Best Practices</li>
			<li>Tech Industry News</li>
		</ul>
		
		<h2>Get in Touch</h2>
		<p>Have a question or suggestion? We'd love to hear from you! Follow us on social media or send us an <a href="mailto:orjidom@yahoo.com">email</a>.</p>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-content {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	h1 {
		color: var(--primary);
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	h2 {
		color: var(--text);
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
	}
	p {
		color: var(--text);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	ul {
		list-style-type: disc;
		margin-left: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	li {
		color: var(--text);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}
</style>